  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the pain at removal of Physiotulle dressing in comparison
      with that of Urgotul dressing in patients presenting a venous (or predominantly) venous leg
      ulcer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
